game.name: Suzy Different Outfit Events
game.description:
Suji looks very excited since she has three unique events to attend today.  Everything is good, but the lady is finding difficulty in finalizing the stylish outfits for these three events. She needs a helping hand. Would you like to test your fashion abilities right away? Join Suzy Different Outfit Events game and be prepared to pick up the perfect dress for each event! The good news is that her wardrobe is full of the trendy and needful dresses so you would not face much difficulty in making the instant decision. 

Your objective in this one of the best HTML5 dressing games is to guide her to prepare for the school, a walk in the park and a walk in the mall. Check out her wardrobe completely to make her look stylish in all the outfits! First of all, she has made out a plan to go to the nearest mall to have a wonderful shopping experience. Give her a casual bob cut hair and dress her up with a denim outfit with buttons and combine it with a pair of sparkling feather shaped earrings,  a golden necklace with colorful pendants, a pair of pink color sandals, a belt around her waist and a purple handbag!

Her next mission is to going to school so try to get her ready then with the help of a red plaid shirt and match it with ripped jeans along with a blue backpack with golden prints, cute flats and simple earrings. Finally she wants to go to the nearest park to visit. Go through her wardrobe and dress her up with a green skirt with buttons on the side, and combine it with a colorful sweater along with a small tea handbag! Check out more dress up games for girls that are free to play online, no download required!
